            "body": "Yes, but the idea was to extend the _API_ common to all such implementations to handle multiple concurrent notifications. Otherwise the producer (calling `vim.notify`) has to do a loop that the consumer (implementing `vim.notify`) has to unroll again. (The motivation is for something like https://neovim.discourse.group/t/wip-animated-notifications-plugin/448.)",
